      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a reliable choice for anyone seeking a practical and functional car. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a quality model at a budget-friendly price point!",
